route-chat-label = Chat
page-chat-summary = Draft prompts, review streamed answers, and keep tool-assisted work visible without leaving the shell.
page-chat-mode = Streaming preview
page-chat-status = Ready for typed backend wiring
page-chat-agenda = Preserve transcript rhythm, prompt composition, and the review loop while replacing ad hoc DOM scripts with Solid state.
page-chat-guardrail = Do not imply tool execution, uploads, or trusted evidence until the gateway endpoints are stable.
