page-jobs-card-b-body = Copy stays explicit about preview-only status so the route never over-claims recovery behaviour.
page-jobs-card-c-title = Evidence hand-off
page-jobs-card-c-body = The route leaves space for durable logs, timestamps, and exit details when the runtime is ready.
