route-extensions-label = Extensions
page-extensions-summary = Separate installed capability, package intake, and external MCP registration behind honest availability states.
page-extensions-mode = Catalogue preview
page-extensions-status = Install flows gated
page-extensions-agenda = Keep the extension route structured around inventories and operator intent instead of raw form sprawl.
page-extensions-guardrail = Installation and removal stay hidden until the runtime can validate packages, auth, and rollback cleanly.
