route-skills-label = Skills
page-skills-summary = Keep discovery, upload, and installation intent together while the backend contract catches up.
page-skills-mode = Library preview
page-skills-status = Install flows gated
page-skills-agenda = Preserve the distinction between searching a catalogue, uploading a bundle, and reviewing installed skills.
page-skills-guardrail = Installation remains disabled until catalogue fetch, bundle upload, and conflict handling are implemented.
